			17.2.6.4: Database Namechange on BaseClaim, UserClaim and RoleClaim
			17.2.6.3: Upgraded to DevExpress v17.2.6
			17.2.5.2: DI Extension methods for .NET Core 2 added and upgraded to DevExpress v17.2.5
